    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202750/extras/1e7f67075f80085ba6277a5eedd471c0.poster.avif?t=1698351035\" width=596 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202750/extras/1e7f67075f80085ba6277a5eedd471c0.webm?t=1698351035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202750/extras/1e7f67075f80085ba6277a5eedd471c0.mp4?t=1698351035\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202750/extras/2d1687b7e913e65b5f6a7a05b61ce56f.webp?t=1698351035\" width=600 height=36 /></span><br><strong>Hardhat Wombat</strong> 是一款可爱的拼图平台构建游戏，它基于世界上最有趣的事实：袋熊有立方体形状的便便。 Doo-doo 尽最大努力巧妙地堆叠便便块并完成越来越复杂的结构。你能成为第二名的第一名吗？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202750/extras/0429270a87fd97138473cb89dc628a98.webp?t=1698351035\" width=615 height=15 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202750/extras/5b7dd8370c074da2efddd61d5e4d724f.webp?t=1698351035\" width=25 height=15 /></span>    在 92 个堆便便的乐趣关卡中拼图和搭建平台！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202750/extras/5b7dd8370c074da2efddd61d5e4d724f.webp?t=1698351035\" width=25 height=15 /></span>    穿越七个世界，每个世界都有自己独特的建筑材料，例如西兰花制成的藤蔓和向上漂浮的口香糖泡泡。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202750/extras/5b7dd8370c074da2efddd61d5e4d724f.webp?t=1698351035\" width=25 height=15 /></span>    遇到各种关卡类型，包括令人费解的炸药关卡和动感十足的甲壳虫狩猎关卡。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202750/extras/5b7dd8370c074da2efddd61d5e4d724f.webp?t=1698351035\" width=25 height=15 /></span>    解锁额外的游戏模式，包括 Daily Gauntlet，您可以在其中与其他玩家竞争袋熊拉屎的霸主地位！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202750/extras/5b7dd8370c074da2efddd61d5e4d724f.webp?t=1698351035\" width=25 height=15 /></span>    来自植物大战僵尸的创造者乔治范！",
